"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 470px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Ultrasonographic appearance of a polycystic ovary in a 15-year-old with PCOS",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 385px; height: 265px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    Ultrasonographic appearance of a polycystic ovary in a 15-year-old with polycystic ovary syndrome (PCOS). Note that in the maximal diameter the ovary is enlarged due to excessive central stroma. In addition, it is polycystic, containing over 10 follicles that are approximately 3 to 8 mm in diameter.",
